Usage: gui_clear_highlight_safety_mechanism [-help] {[-dcls  | -tmr  | -ser ]}

-help     # Prints out the command usage
-dcls     # Dehighlight all dcls group's insts, internal-nets, interface-nets,
          # common-nets and top-nets (bool, required)
-ser      # Dehighlight all ser insts (bool, required)
-tmr      # Dehighlight all tmr parents, tmr clones and tmr voters
          # (bool, required)